r62998 | nagachika | 2018-03-28 19:52:33 +0900 (Wed, 28 Mar 2018) | 5 lines

merge revision(s) 62990:

	Ignore file separator from tmpfile/tmpdir name.

	From: SHIBATA Hiroshi <hsbt@ruby-lang.org>
