merge revision(s) 58453,58454: [Backport #13499]

	Fix space flag when Inf/NaN and width==3

	* sprintf.c (rb_str_format): while `"% 2f"` and `"% 4f"` result in
	  `" Inf"` and `" Inf"` respectively, `"% 3f"` results in
	  `"Inf"` (no space).
